description: I was so excited to participate in the #30DayMapChallenge I totally missed that it starts in November and not, like, right now. Uh. Maybe you want to know how close you are to a ballot drop box anyway?

I am definitely not doing the #30DayMapChallenge because there is an election. But since the first day's theme was points (it's still the first day in Hawaii) and I was thinking about polling booth locations here's all of them. It's essentially population density but ü§∑‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è
